G4 - TV That's Plugged In
X-Play - February 4th, 2009 (re-air)

Who Will Watch The Fallout?

In this episode of X-Play, Adam and Morgan take to the streets with Rorschach to check out The Watchmen: The End is Nigh for Xbox 360 and PlayStation 3, including over 7 minutes of never before seen gameplay, two new levels and co-op gameplay. Then, Kristin Adams delivers tips for finding Death Cards in Call of Duty: World at War in Cheat. Plus, we let you know what new Fallout 3 levels to grab in The Download, take you to X-Play Orientation, deliver a Gaming Update and more!
